# Vendor Management System
Simple rest apis to provide functionalities to vendors to place order and manage audits.

### Prerequisites

- Python 3.8+
- Django 4.2

### Installing

A step-by-step series of examples that tell you how to get a development environment running.

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/Rahul-Radheshyam-Gupta/vendor_management_system.git

# Change into the project directory
cd vendor_management_system

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Create virtual environment
- Install toot to create virtual env: -sudo apt install virtualenv
virtualenv env
source env/bin/activate

# Migrate databases
python manage.py makemigrations
python manage.py migrate

# Run  django development server on local
python manage.py runserver
